          <!-- Item -->
          <div class="item">
            <a href="#" class="thumb"><img src="images/solution-4-thumb.png" /></a>
            <h3><a href="#">Contests, sweepstakes and games</a></h3>
            <p>Make shopping even more fun! Engage your customers with a wide range of competitions to give your loyalty programs a word-of-mouth boost.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Find out more</a>
          </div>

          <div class="clear"><!-- --></div>
